# Sokolovskoye, Republic of Bashkortostan

}}
Sokolovskoye () is a rural locality (a village) in Ilyino-Polyansky Selsoviet, Blagoveshchensky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 63 as of 2010. There are 2 streets.
Geography
Sokolovskoye is located 33 km east of Blagoveshchensk (the district's administrative centre) by road. Sitniki is the nearest rural locality.
